Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(410.717,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I thought we should resume baseball practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:35.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,which we all forgot about,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but since the horse is tearing up the field,\Nwe'll call it off for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:39.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,First and foremost, people\N shouldn't bring horses to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:48.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:48.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Kokuryu's smart, so he can understand human words.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't make light of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:54.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're very smart and if\Nyou're friendly to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they do things like\Nsoothe your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:01.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's possible that they may soothe\Neveryone's currently hardened hearts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Animals really are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't the horse what\N irritated you in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:11.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And then, we hastily\N founded an animal lovers club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:14.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and decided that everyone\N will bring their pets to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow, people brought a variety of pets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I brought a typical pet, a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's cute. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Taro. It's a little too commonplace, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Speaking of names, my name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, then, let's move onto the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to bring a lion\Nas proof of my kingship,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it got held up due to\Nthe Washington Convention,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so I brought just a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's just like you, Hokuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? You didn't bring anything, Maeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I brought a hamster,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it was eaten by Hayashida's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My condolences...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, there are many different things happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:54.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I'm glad to know that\N everyone has the heart to love animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you have a heart that\Nloves and adores animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you should be able to be kind to others too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:03.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Who's that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We can't tell which one is the pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That one's the pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,390)\bord0.1}Maeda, changing straw bedding for horse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to take care of the pets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who suggested\Nhaving pets in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you complaining about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if you're dissatisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,deal with it after you complete your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:33.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If all you do is complain instead of working, \Npeople will think you're useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's not a complaint! I'm just\Nstating my reasonable opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll ask you, have you ever\Ngone to vote in an election?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,392)\bord0.1}Akira Maeda (16) No voting rights!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Voting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I've never gone to vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,See, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You must be thinking\N "my vote won't change anything," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if there are only people like you,\Nsociety won't make progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:53.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But, there are tons of people in society
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who are more irresponsible than I am.\NThat's why Japan is getting bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying is bad about Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Share prices have fallen\Nand the yen has dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And the Japanese economy is failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There isn't a single good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:15.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you saying that if the yen weakens,\Nit will influence your life somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that, but there isn't anything good about the yen getting weaker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, if the yen is too expensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the Japanese companies that\Nexpanded overseas will take a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't speak as if you know everything\Nby seeing only one side of the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In my view, you're only\N repeating what's in the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, you may be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In that case, you're only speaking\N others' opinions like they're your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why don't you look around and talk about the\Nthings closer to you that you're dissatisfied with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see... Complaints closer to me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When I get home,\N the first thing I do is take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You know bath mats, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The ones you use to dry your feet after a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fnArnold 2.1\move(572.12,36,563.057,47,0,1732)\c&HBCBD96&\bord1.5\3c&H394D56&\blur0.4\shad0\fs26}This one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My old lady washes this\N bath mat every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it shouldn't get very dirty\Nsince you use it to dry your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,after washing your body clean in the bath, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I don't think it's necessary\Nto wash it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think it's okay to wash it about once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It also saves water and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're saying that since your feet \Nare clean after a bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you don't have to wash the bath mat every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But what about before you take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I step on the mat with dirty feet\Nbefore taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was only thinking about\N when I get out of the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's what I tried to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looking at just one side of the issue isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we clear up the problems\None by one like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Japan will be a better place, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The sun shines lightly through\Nthe gap in the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,as if it proclaims the arrival of winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. You wanna eat?\NI'll prepare it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Strangely enough, when you take care of\Nanimals for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you start to understand how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're hungry too? Hold on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel relaxed when I'm with these guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:28.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Somehow I feel that, for the first time,\NI've found a place where I feel peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Behave yourselves until tomorrow as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll clean the stable and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What in the hell am I doing this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Far from being soothed,\NI was almost brainwashed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:49.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I carelessly let my guard down and\N came to like the animals before I knew it! Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moreover, it's already time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What am I still at school for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:57.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I never said one word about\Nraising pets in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I sincerely feel bad about\N what we've done to you, Maeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To put it simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,since we're already bored with our pets\Nwe're thinking about getting rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!\NI'll fudgin' kill you morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You guys are always like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You get all excited about things \Nand then quickly get bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Same thing with baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to go to Koshien,\N but you don't care at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You haven't gotten any better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie can now pitch at 160 km/h, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But he's taking forever to learn the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\N he hit a ball and ran to third base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel sorry for the animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought\Nfrom the animals' perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if you tell us to put\Nourselves in animals' shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,we're not animals, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,See, I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You guys are just thinking\Nabout yourselves after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Maeda, since we're humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it's impossible to put\N ourselves in animal's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For example, what should\NI do to make a cat happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, if you stroke its head\N like this, it'll be happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Did you ask the cats about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No... I certainly haven't\Nasked them about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:09.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words, the idea that a cat is happy when you stroke it is a baseless assumption made by humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and they might actually hate it because it tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:17.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then... the idea that the animals that I took\Ncare of were happy was also my assumption?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:21.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you can't say with confidence\Nthat you understand how cats feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,can you say you understand how animals feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So my interaction with them was\Nmy own baseless assumption?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:31.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And why am I being scolded\N by people who didn't take care of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I'm pretty sure the animals\Nand I understood each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just\N become a cat once and for all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Become a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you can perfectly understand how cats feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll admit that humans and animals\Ncan understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Prove to me that you can \Nput yourself in animals' shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But... even if you suddenly\Ntell me to become a cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:52.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Indeed, even if I suddenly tell you\Nto become a cat, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll give you just one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,392)}Maeda's house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No... this isn't what it's about, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:12.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\bord0\blur0.4\c&HE1E3E9&\pos(254.905,351)}Rice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:12.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\bord0\c&HEBF3FE&\blur0.4\pos(525.671,171)}Dried Bonito
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:08.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As a first step, I started adding a dish of\Ndried bonito to my meals yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but besides becoming a cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it's very good because it helps\Nmake a well-balanced diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What else do I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'd be good to put on a bell, nyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll try adding "nya" at the end of sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:22.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Nyo" is a gazillion times\Nbetter than "nya," nyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good morning... {\alphaFF}nya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good morning... nya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm an ordinary high school student... {\alphaff}nya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm an ordinary high school student... nya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:34.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Aren't I just passing myself off as a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:39.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And thus one week was gone,\Nwithout anything to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,M-Maeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You grew quite skinny...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:49.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I finally got what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard we humans try,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,in the end, there's no way that\N we can understand how animals feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It was impossible to become a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're already a fine cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why can't people understand how animals feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's because humans have egos and arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But you've just noticed that! You'll be fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks... I finally... did it, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well done, Maeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So what should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? I think you should\N be your usual self, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. I felt relieved to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Were you seriously thinking of\Nbecoming a cat by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can I take these off now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&)}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I thought that was the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't take these off, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:44.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
