Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\shad0\c&HFFEDFF&\3c&HD969F9&\bord3\blur0.5\pos(137.082,184)}Dejiko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\shad0\c&HFFEDFF&\3c&HD969F9&\bord3\blur0.5\pos(335.342,300)}Puchiko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you get too carried away just because\Nyour joke was a little popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,people won't be faithful to you and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:42.38,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\an7\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz90\pos(11.329,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:42.38,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\an9\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz270\pos(704.671,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.38,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz90\pos(11.329,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.38,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz270\pos(704.671,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:43.80,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an7\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz90\pos(11.329,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:43.80,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an9\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz270\pos(704.671,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:43.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so get a grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I recommend "nyo" at the end of sentences, nyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Nyu" is okay too, nyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Nyo...
